# RxJS Services

Follow `rxjs-patterns` (`.cursor/skills/rxjs-patterns/SKILL.md`).

- HTTP via `get$`/`getAnon$` in `core/http.ts` — never raw `fetch`
- Return `Observable<T>`, not `Promise<T>`
- `take(1)` for one-shot; `shareReplay(1)` for shared streams; `switchMap` to cancel stale requests
- Status: `'initial' | 'loading' | 'success' | 'error'` + `error: unknown`
